FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:8080/api

# Library API
Library management service.

# Books [/books]
### List Books [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Book])

### Create Book [POST]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (Book)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Book)

# Data Structures
## Book (object)
+ id: 1 (number, required)
+ title: "Python Programming" (string, required)
+ author: "Nguyen Van A" (string)